text: Brrda phu ptiseth kar sraththa thang ca kxah lu lki tap læa cak brrda mu chri knan tang mi chxb thi ca hı mi khwam di dı «cak phracea khxng phwk cea thuk prathan lng ma kæ phwk cea læa xallxha nan ca thrng ceaacng khwam kruna khxng phraxngkh kæ phu thi phraxngkh thrng pra sngkh læa xallxh nan pen phu mi buy khun xan hıy hlwng
